     =========================================================
     Geant4 - an Object-Oriented Toolkit for Simulation in HEP
     =========================================================

                      Benchmarks module
                      -----------------

This module collects a set of "bechmark" tests which are used as part of the
validation procedure, to verify and control the overall CPU performance of
the GEANT4 toolkit. Each test may include more than one test case, covering
different initial conditions and setups.
This set of tests is going to be extended in future, to become more and more
exhaustive and complete.

ANY change or update to the source code or input macros MUST be notified to
the System Testing (geant4-stt@cern.ch), specifying if these will affect the
measurements in comparison to previous benchmark runs, meaning that it may be
necessary to regenerate all reference measurements.

